11:42.900 --> 11:46.100
He was standing across the street
before the car exploded.

11:46.200 --> 11:50.600
- The police said he was there all morning.
- Right. Christine said she never saw him before.

11:50.700 --> 11:53.700
- How about you?
- No, sorry. What about the letters?

11:53.800 --> 11:55.900
Well, i'm gonna see captain
stottlemeyer later today.

11:56.000 --> 11:57.900
