My god.

19:33.400 --> 19:37.300
Oh...my...god.

19:38.100 --> 19:40.500
- You okay?
- This is horrible.

19:40.800 --> 19:42.900
It's horrible.
What are you drinking?

19:43.000 --> 19:45.200
- Tea.
- Is it hot?

19:45.300 --> 19:47.900
- Yes.
- Good. Pour it into my eyes.

19:48.000 --> 19:50.100
- Mr. Monk.
- Do it, blind me.

19:50.200 --> 19:51.800
You know what,
she's an actress.

19:51.900 --> 19:55.000
They all have problems,
especially when they start that young.

19:55.100 --> 19:56.200
Judy garland--

19:56.300 --> 19:58.800
- What is that?
- I don't know.

19:58.900 --> 20:00.400
Thank you for not knowing.

20:00.500 --> 20:02.000
You're welcome.

20:02.300 --> 20:05.300
This is unbelievable. Of course
someone's trying to kill her.

20:05.400 --> 20:07.200
Anyone she's ever
met has a motive.

20:07.300 --> 20:10.200
Anyone who's ever
read this has a motive.

